1
00:00:00,582 --> 00:00:02,147
Get tactical, Marines!

2
00:00:02,307 --> 00:00:06,021
Major ? Allez sur ce cargo et capturez-moi ce Prophète du Regret.

3
00:00:06,118 --> 00:00:11,719
This is the only place on Earth the Covenant decided to land. That prophet is going to tell us why.

4
00:00:07,570 --> 00:00:10,995
You heard the man, boys. It's time for some hazard pay!

5
00:00:15,063 --> 00:00:17,191
Thirty seconds out. Stand by to…

6
00:00:18,546 --> 00:00:19,046
Whoah!

7
00:01:00,816 --> 00:01:01,316
Status!

8
00:01:02,064 --> 00:01:04,040
Sir? O'Brien's down.

9
00:01:04,785 --> 00:01:06,418
We lost our pilots, too.

10
00:01:07,237 --> 00:01:08,708
Grab their tags and ammo.

11
00:01:08,959 --> 00:01:09,459
Sarge!

12
00:01:10,463 --> 00:01:11,657
We better get moving.

13
00:01:12,332 --> 00:01:15,094
Agreed. We'll find better cover in those buildings.

14
00:01:15,897 --> 00:01:17,462
Butkis, you take point.

15
00:01:40,269 --> 00:01:40,769
Hello!

16
00:01:42,174 --> 00:01:43,882
Sniper, third floor, left.

17
00:01:43,967 --> 00:01:47,233
Here…let me give them my "Welcome to Earth" gift basket!

18
00:02:13,899 --> 00:02:14,399
Whoah!

19
00:02:18,697 --> 00:02:19,798
Damn, where is he?

20
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:28,628
Anybody see him?

21
00:02:45,196 --> 00:02:46,216
Take him, guys!

22
00:02:48,678 --> 00:02:49,834
Cook the bastard.

23
00:02:55,812 --> 00:02:58,724
Second squad, this is Cortana. What is your status, over.

24
00:02:59,038 --> 00:03:00,903
We're operational, ma'am…barely.

25
00:03:01,021 --> 00:03:02,208
Our pilots didn't make it.

26
00:03:02,312 --> 00:03:04,779
Find a hole, stay put. We'll come to you.

